ENTRY       EC 2.4.1.118                Enzyme
NAME        cytokinin 7-beta-glucosyltransferase;
            uridine diphosphoglucose-zeatin 7-glucosyltransferase;
            cytokinin 7-glucosyltransferase;
            UDP-glucose:zeatin 7-glucosyltransferase
CLASS       Transferases;
            Glycosyltransferases;
            Hexosyltransferases
SYSNAME     UDP-glucose:N6-alkylaminopurine 7-glucosyltransferase
REACTION    UDP-glucose + an N6-alkylaminopurine = UDP + an N6-alkylaminopurine-7-beta-D-glucoside [RN:R04071]
ALL_REAC    R04071;
            (other) R08369
SUBSTRATE   UDP-glucose [CPD:C00029];
            N6-alkylaminopurine [CPD:C02860]
PRODUCT     UDP [CPD:C00015];
            N6-alkylaminopurine-7-beta-D-glucoside [CPD:C04422]
COMMENT     Acts on a range of N6-substituted adenines, including zeatin and N6-benzylaminopurine, but not N6-benzyladenine. With some acceptors, 9-beta-D-glucosides are also formed.
HISTORY     EC 2.4.1.118 created 1984
